Benchmark European coal prices
advanced for a third consecutive session.  Thermal coal for delivery to Amsterdam, Rotterdam or
Antwerp with settlement next year rose 50 cents, or 0.4 percent,
to $129.50 a metric ton as of 11:14 a.m. in  London , according to
broker prices compiled by Bloomberg. Thatâ€™s the highest intraday
price since Aug. 1.  Bloomberg tracks data from information supplied by ICAP
